{"tid":1421084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"捉到打人白衣點做？","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:12:33.000Z","uid":281463,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"967116c37f0fe6ca252fe9e3a7561a70bbb20b05","tid":1421084,"uid":281463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"發夢捉到打人白衣點做？<br />\n<br />\n切勿亂柒毒打頭部及身體<br />\n有老坑有白粉佬<br />\n<br />\n捉住佢綁起雙腳，雙手雙腳請以甩臼骨折為基本<br />\n綁佢做人肉路障，側邊加句與民為敵紙牌<br />\n<br />\n1.好處，唔會打死人，為左垃圾被告謀殺唔抵<br />\n2.風險極高增加佢地出勤費用<br />\n3.打石膏至少三個月出唔返黎，可減少前線被襲<br />\n4.羞辱老黑<br />\n<br />\n以上發夢咋，犯法野咪做"},{"pid":"6a9ddf1a2776191ee362c30dce1b89498296bea0","tid":1421084,"uid":189157,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"綁住佢送上前線等佢用生命值硬接彈"},{"pid":"95498e94eb187c088bd32d194ad47c0fc0b03640","tid":1421084,"uid":29880,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:53:56.000Z","msg":"綁手綁腳<br />\n影低個樣"},{"pid":"1e356ac72189cf5d60086e171b53b9b7df0bc96c","tid":1421084,"uid":281463,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6a9ddf1a2776191ee362c30dce1b89498296bea0","tid":1421084,"uid":189157,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"綁住佢送上前線等佢用生命值硬接彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"除撚埋佢條褲"},{"pid":"1ca765fb16cf019f286202c224900ef9ac16a46b","tid":1421084,"uid":281463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95498e94eb187c088bd32d194ad47c0fc0b03640","tid":1421084,"uid":29880,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:53:56.000Z","msg":"綁手綁腳<br />\n影低個樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"綁手綁腳，我要佢斷手斷腳"},{"pid":"934a454c5912fa245d34b9d14bc1cd7721ff4cd2","tid":1421084,"uid":107656,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"隔離po話要錫春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fe9e94d444c436d3fe